org.eng.aisp.dataset

Interface ISoundDataSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDereferencer<String,SoundRecording>, IDoubleDataSet<SoundRecording>, IItemReferenceIterable<SoundRecording>, ILabeledDataSet<double[],SoundRecording>, IShuffleIterable<SoundRecording>, ISizedIterable<SoundRecording>, Iterable<SoundRecording>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComposedSoundDataSet, ComposedStoredSoundDataSet

    public interface ISoundDataSet
extends IDoubleDataSet<SoundRecording>
    Holds a set of sound references with associated labeling, tagging and other data. Allows both shuffleable iteration and direct access to the contained references via IItemReferenceIterable.dereference(String). The data set may be examined in total to get the full set of contained label names and label values for any of the contained label names.
